Design Handles by Valli&Valli
Valli & Valli, leading Italian manufacturer of design handles, offers the best selection of handles and doors accessories. The design of Valli&Valli and Fusital collections are unique. From contemporary to classic handles, each handle is carefully designed to perfectly fit your environment.













Valli&Valli broad range of classic and contemporary handles designed by Valli Workshop.
Discover the range


The Fusital collections have been designed by the most important international architects and designer.
