References and Projects

		Take a look to the awesome Valli&Valli projects 
	






Carbon Trust verified

		Valli&Valli's primary factory site, in Renate, has achieved verification from the Carbon Trust that it provides a zero waste to landfill operation! Valli&Valli constantly improving the optimization of product components and reduction of waste at every stage of the product lifecycle. The verification was conducted in accordance with the measurement requirements of the Corporate Waste Assessment Protocol. 
	


